## Env variables this repo expects.
## Copy this file to `.env` and fill values.

## ---- Azure OpenAI (used by rag_cli.py and some pipeline scripts) ----
## Prefer setting AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY; some legacy scripts still read OPENAI_API_KEY.
AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY=your-azure-openai-api-key-here

## Provide ONE of the following:
## Option A: endpoint (resource root). rag_cli.py will derive base_url = <endpoint>/openai/v1/
AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT=https://<your-resource-name>.openai.azure.com/
## Option B: explicit OpenAI-compatible base URL (often ends with /openai/v1/)
# AZURE_OPENAI_BASE_URL=https://<your-resource-name>.openai.azure.com/openai/v1/

## Azure deployment names
AZURE_OPENAI_DEPLOYMENT=gpt-4o
AZURE_OPENAI_EMBEDDING_DEPLOYMENT=text-embedding-3-small

## ---- Legacy / fallback (keep for older scripts) ----
OPENAI_API_KEY=your-openai-or-azure-key-here

## ---- Mistral (optional, only if you run mistral model_type) ----
MISTRAL_API_KEY=your-mistral-api-key-here

